You are working on the Bevelled website.

Rules:
- Framework: Next.js (App Router), TypeScript
- Styling: TailwindCSS + shadcn
- CMS: Supabase
- Email: Resend
- Always run:
  - pnpm lint
  - pnpm check
  - pnpm build
  - pnpm test (Playwright e2e)
before committing any changes.
- Do not accept commits if e2e tests fail.
